  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study evaluate the cognitive functions of patient after hip or kneel replacement.Half of
      the patient will receive transcutaneous vagus nerve electrical stimulation during the surgery
      while the other half will get placebo therapy
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
